      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "As an additional hint in case you are debugging your unit tests: <code>gradle assemble</code> will not compile the main files. If you work in getting your unit test fixed then  you need <code>gradle assemble testClasses</code> — I think that the build task naming is quite confusing."
