    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Try:</p>\n\n<pre><code>gradle assemble\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>To list all available tasks for your project, try:</p>\n\n<pre><code>gradle tasks\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>UPDATE:</p>\n\n<p>This may not seem the most correct answer at first, but read carefully <code>gradle tasks</code> output or docs.</p>\n\n<pre><code>Build tasks\n-----------\nassemble - Assembles the outputs of this project.\nbuild - Assembles and tests this project.\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
