      "comment_id" : 41291636,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "For me this is still the only working option as the -x test seems to only work on the starting project but not for dependencies in a multi project build (tested on gradle 2.1). Put the test.onlyif ... in a configure(subprojects.findAll {javaProjects.contains(it.name)}) {} block in your root build.gradle and it will work for all projects."
    } ],
    "owner" : {
