  "question_id" : 4597850,
  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4597850/gradle-build-without-tests",
  "title" : "Gradle build without tests",
  "body" : "<p>I want to execute <code>gradle build</code> without executing the unit tests. I tried:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-bash prettyprint-override\"><code>gradle -Dskip.tests build\n</code></pre>\n<p>That doesn't seem to do anything. Is there some other command I could use?</p>\n"
